information.transcription:
Cannon Mills Company. 1906. 
Textile mill founded in Kannapolis, North Carolina.
Originally known as  the Cannon Manufacturing company.

Company produced textiles, principally towels.
It became the largest textile company in the world.

It became the largest producer of towels in the world
More than 1,000,000 towels daily.
